  <name>Elelem</name>
  <summary>A friendly assistant with LLM</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Elelem is a versatile LLM client that connects seamlessly with OpenAI API compatible
      services. Effortlessly create and switch between multiple custom prompts to match your needs.
      Open source and cross platform, Elelem puts control in your hands with your own API key;
      without it you can't use the app.</p>
  </description>
